QuestData.Title: Felblaze Ingress
QuestData.Description: It is my mission to cover the rear guard of Illidari Stand. I have employed this warlock... thing, to assist me.$b$bHowever, the two of us are insufficient for a task that needs doing.$b$bTo the east is a mass of demons at Felblaze Ingress. These creatures have begun to open portals to summon in countless reinforcements.$b$bMeet us at Felblaze Ingress and together we can crush this fel insurgency.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Tehd Shoemaker at Felblaze Ingress.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Tehd Shoemaker at Felblaze Ingress.
QuestData.RewardText: Keep your voice down unless you feel like being felbat food.
